  "description": "Kundenbewertungen in Karten-Layout",
  "template": "<section class=\"{{spacing}} bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white\">\n  <div class=\"{{containerWidth}} mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[{{accentColor}}]/10 text-[{{accentColor}}] px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n        <span class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-sm\">4.9 von 5 Sternen</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl {{fontFamily}} {{fontWeight}} mb-4 text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n        Das sagen unsere Mitglieder\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"text-lg text-[{{textColor}}]/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n        Echte Erfahrungen von echten Menschen – keine gekauften Bewertungen\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n      <div class=\"group bg-white p-8 rounded-[{{borderRadius}}] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[{{primaryColor}}]\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[{{accentColor}}] text-xl mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-quote-left text-4xl text-[{{primaryColor}}]/20\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/80 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed mb-8 italic\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          \"Bestes Gym in der Region! Die Atmosphäre ist familiär und man fühlt sich sofort wohl. Keine nervigen Verkaufsgespräche wie bei den großen Ketten. Einfach trainieren und sich wohlfühlen!\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100\">\n          <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white {{fontWeight}} text-xl\">\n            MM\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Max Müller</p>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Mitglied seit 2020</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"group bg-white p-8 rounded-[{{borderRadius}}] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[{{primaryColor}}]\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[{{accentColor}}] text-xl mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-quote-left text-4xl text-[{{primaryColor}}]/20\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/80 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed mb-8 italic\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          \"Hier trainiere ich seit 5 Jahren und würde nirgendwo anders hingehen. Authentisch, ehrlich, oldschool - genau so muss ein Gym sein! Die Community ist einfach top.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100\">\n          <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white {{fontWeight}} text-xl\">\n            JS\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Julia Schmidt</p>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Mitglied seit 2018</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"group bg-white p-8 rounded-[{{borderRadius}}] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[{{primaryColor}}]\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[{{accentColor}}] text-xl mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-star\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mb-6\">\n          <i class=\"fa-solid fa-quote-left text-4xl text-[{{primaryColor}}]/20\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/80 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed mb-8 italic\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          \"Top Ausstattung, faire Preise und keine Vertragslaufzeiten die dich binden. Man kennt sich und hilft sich gegenseitig. Einfach perfekt für alle, die ernsthaft trainieren wollen!\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100\">\n          <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white {{fontWeight}} text-xl\">\n            TW\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Tim Wagner</p>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Mitglied seit 2021</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
}
